
---

### **2. main_APISignalPath**  
**Description:**  
Monitors API endpoints for latency and signal variation, visualizing response changes over request paths.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APISignalPath - Endpoint Drift & Health Monitor

APISignalPath visualizes latency trends and signal consistency across tracked endpoints over time.

## Features
- Drift + error tracking  
- Real-time and batch mode  
- Export to JSON / CSV  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_APISignalPath.git
cd main_APISignalPath
python monitor.py

